@startuml web-patch-cost-summary
!theme plain
!include ../shared/theme.puml

title Cost of Web Patch Strategy (and Mitigations)

rectangle "Cost / Risk" as C1 #FFECEC
rectangle "Observed Impact" as C2 #FFF7E6
rectangle "Mitigation Used" as C3 #EAF7EA

C1 -down-> C2
C2 -down-> C3

note right of C1
1) Extra integration complexity
2) Maintenance overhead for patch layer
3) Temporary dependency on author fork
end note

note right of C2
1) More moving parts to debug
2) Higher regression risk during updates
3) Upstream lag can block cleanup
end note

note right of C3
1) Kept manager-level API stable
2) Added logging + isolated web patch modules
3) Submitted upstream PR and tracked merge path
end note

legend right
|= Dimension |= Interpretation |
| Complexity | Additional components and boundaries |
| Maintenance | Ongoing effort to keep patch compatible |
| Dependency | Operational reliance until upstream integration |
endlegend

@enduml

